@@ -0,0 +1,11 @@
+## Overview
+
+Niantic fork of node-gles. Changes made here should be diffed against the original origin
+and then added as a patch to repo/niantic.
+
+# For a new clone, add the original origin.
+git remote add old-origin https://github.com/google/node-gles.git
+git fetch
+
+# Compute and save the patch to repo/niantic.
+git diff old-origin/master > ../niantic/third_party/node-gles/node-gles.patch
